## A1: Pipeline Progress Format

Display at the start of subagent/teams mode and after each Phase transition in the `go` subcommand.

```
рҹҗҷ Pipeline в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ
  вң“ Phase 1: Planning
  вҶ’ Phase 2: Implementation [N/M tasks]
  в—Ӣ Phase 3: Testing
  в—Ӣ Phase 4: Review
```

**Status symbols:**
- `вң“` вҖ” Phase completed successfully
- `вҶ’` вҖ” Current active phase
- `в—Ӣ` вҖ” Phase pending

**Rules:**
- Replace `[N/M tasks]` with actual completed/total task counts (e.g., `[3/7 tasks]`)
- Update the display after each phase transition
- Always show all 4 phases regardless of current position

