## A2: Workflow Lifecycle Format

Display after each subcommand (plan, go, sync) completes to show position in the full cycle.

```
рҹҗҷ Workflow: {SPEC-ID}
  вң“ plan  вҶ’  в—Ҹ go  вҶ’  в—Ӣ sync
```

**Status symbols:**
- `вң“` вҖ” Stage completed
- `в—Ҹ` вҖ” Current stage (just completed)
- `в—Ӣ` вҖ” Stage pending

**Stage combinations:**

After `plan` completes:
```
рҹҗҷ Workflow: {SPEC-ID}
  в—Ҹ plan  вҶ’  в—Ӣ go  вҶ’  в—Ӣ sync
```

After `go` completes:
```
рҹҗҷ Workflow: {SPEC-ID}
  вң“ plan  вҶ’  в—Ҹ go  вҶ’  в—Ӣ sync
```

After `sync` completes:
```
рҹҗҷ Workflow: {SPEC-ID}
  вң“ plan  вҶ’  вң“ go  вҶ’  в—Ҹ sync
```

**With idea stage** (when `--from-idea` or `--idea` flag is used):

After `idea` completes:
```
рҹҗҷ Workflow: BS-{ID}
  в—Ҹ idea  вҶ’  в—Ӣ plan  вҶ’  в—Ӣ go  вҶ’  в—Ӣ sync
```

After `plan` completes (from idea):
```
рҹҗҷ Workflow: BS-{ID} вҶ’ {SPEC-ID}
  вң“ idea  вҶ’  в—Ҹ plan  вҶ’  в—Ӣ go  вҶ’  в—Ӣ sync
```

After `go` completes (from idea):
```
рҹҗҷ Workflow: BS-{ID} вҶ’ {SPEC-ID}
  вң“ idea  вҶ’  вң“ plan  вҶ’  в—Ҹ go  вҶ’  в—Ӣ sync
```

After `sync` completes (from idea):
```
рҹҗҷ Workflow: BS-{ID} вҶ’ {SPEC-ID}
  вң“ idea  вҶ’  вң“ plan  вҶ’  вң“ go  вҶ’  в—Ҹ sync
```

**With discover stage** (when `/auto discover` is used):

After `discover` completes:
```
рҹҗҷ Workflow: BS-{ID}
  в—Ҹ discover  вҶ’  в—Ӣ plan  вҶ’  в—Ӣ go  вҶ’  в—Ӣ sync
```

After `plan` completes (from discover):
```
рҹҗҷ Workflow: BS-{ID} вҶ’ {SPEC-ID}
  вң“ discover  вҶ’  в—Ҹ plan  вҶ’  в—Ӣ go  вҶ’  в—Ӣ sync
```

